Motor Board
===========

The motor board is used to connect a motor to your kit. A diagram of the major parts you need to know about is pictured below:

![motor board diagram](images/content/kit/motor_board_diagram.png "The Motor Board")

Initial Power-up State
----------------------

* Power LED &mdash; on
* Token LED &mdash; on
* Motor power LED &mdash; off
* Current limit LED &mdash; off
* Feedback LEDs &mdash; off
* Motor direction LEDs &mdash; off

After you have started your code the `Motor power LED` should come on and the `Current Limit LED` remain off.
